Create a blog with the following use cases

Admin and superadmin priviledges
The admin registration must be approved by the superadmin
Registration for an author must be approved by the admin or superadmin
Other users are the author and commentators 
Registration of a commentator does not need approval
Their should be a password reset functionality


An author, admin and superadmins can write blogs
An image can be uploaded to a blog and associated to a particular blog
A blog can be deleted by an admin or superadmin
A blog must have atleast one image
A blog can be rated by a user who is not logged in


A comment can be rated by a user who is logged in
A comment can be deleted by an admin or superadmin
A user can view all comments associated to a particular post by pagination


Posts and comments associated to the post can be viewed by pagination
Posts can be categorised into categories
Only an admin or superadmin can create a category of a post
A user can veiw all posts from a particular category with pagination
Their should be a date when a post or comment was made

Admins and superdadmins should be able to view all authors
superadmins should be able to block an author from making posts
Admins and superadmins should have the capacity to block a commentator
Superadmins should have the capacity to list all admins
Admins cannot view superadmins

users should be able to log in using their gmail, yahoo and such o
Add search functionality

Use flask as the backend


